# -*- mode: org; -*-

This file contains common HTML export settings for org-mode.

** Disable table of contents and header numbering

   #+Options: toc:nil num:nil html_postamble:nil
   # (setq org-html-postamble nil)

** Include google font

   #+HTML_HEAD: <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

** Use custom CSS

   It's important to note that the link is relative _from_ the
   sub-directory (where the overviews are stored).
   
   #+HTML_HEAD: <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="overview.css"> <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../overview.css">
   #+HTML_HEAD: <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="overview.css"> <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../../../overview.css">
